Title: 'Evolution: The Ride'
DateModified: '2019-02-19'
DatePublished: '2019-02-19'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/evolution-the-ride
SetInCountry: Australia
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Anthony Parker
AuthorCountry: Australia
Text: An epic tale of discovery, exploration and the realization of a 10 year dream.  It
  is a journey across the rugged shipwreck coast and surrounding areas of Australia's
  southern Victorian coastline, traveling across the Great Ocean Road by Motorcycle,
  experiencing the ocean air, the sights, sounds and smells as you become one with
  the terrain, become one with the environment, and encounter the beauty and wonder
  of this stunning location.
